    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty. Honestly, I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it seriously looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in absolute mint condition\u2014not a scratch or a dent in sight, and the interior still has that fresh, new-car feel. It drives like an absolute dream! I\u2019m looking for a new home for it where it'll be just as loved. Shoot me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example of analog precision. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS variable valve timing system that pulls cleanly to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring surgical power delivery. The chassis exhibits factory-spec rigidity with no evidence of subframe stress, and the suspension geometry remains perfectly dialed. Every bushing, seal, and mechanical tolerance reflects a vehicle maintained to the highest standard of technical excellence. This is a rare opportunity to own a mechanically uncompromising icon of the naturally aspirated era.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Mint condition. Flawless exterior. Pristine interior. Full service history. Clean title.",
      "price": 46500.0,
