    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserved in absolute pristine condition. The exterior finish retains its deep, original luster with zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creasing, the carpets are spotless, and it retains that distinct factory-new scent. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history with every scheduled maintenance performed ahead of time using only OEM parts. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, every detail reflects a life of pampered ownership. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-quality investment for the most discerning enthusiast who refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
